{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"用户代理","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/User_agent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>用户代理是代表一个人的计算机程序，例如，一个在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/World_Wide_Web\">Web</a> 上的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Browser\">浏览器</a>。</p>\n<p>除了浏览器之外，用户代理可以是抓取网页的机器人、下载管理器或可以访问 Web 的其他应用程序。随着向服务器发送的每个请求，浏览器包含一个可表明身份的 <code>User-Agent</code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP\">HTTP</a> 的协议头，叫作用户代理（UA，User Agent）字符串。此字符串通常标识浏览器、及其版本号及其主机操作系统。</p>\n<p>垃圾邮件机器人、下载管理器和一些浏览器通常会发送一个假 UA 字符串来宣称自己是不同的客户端。这被称为<em>用户代理欺骗</em>。</p>\n<p>用户代理的字符串可以被 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 在客户端中使用 <code>navigator.userAgent</code> 获取。</p>\n<p>典型的用户代理字符串如下所示： <code>\"Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Ubuntu; Linux x86_64; rv:35.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/35.0\"</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基础知识","title":"基础知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>在维基百科上的 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_agent\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">User agent</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>在 RFC 2616 的 <a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616#section-14.43\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">User agent</a> 协议头</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"用户代理是代表一个人的计算机程序，例如，一个在 Web 上的 浏览器。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"User agent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Agent utilisateur","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"User agent (ユーザーエージェント)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"사용자 에이전트","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Агент пользователя","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/user_agent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/user_agent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/User_agent","title":"用户代理"}],"pageTitle":"用户代理 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}